***** REVENANT *****

Name:          Revenant
Kind:          Spell
Target:        Object (NPC corpse in room)
Position:      Standing
Min Mana:      75
Wait Beats:    24
Can Learn:     No

Acquisition:   Necromancer level 70, Ego level 70

Description:
   Raises a permanent undead minion (revenant) from an NPC corpse.
   The revenant inherits the original mob's full combat statistics,
   capped at the caster's pseudo level (hard cap 150).

   Better corpses produce stronger revenants.  Use the 'revenant'
   command to manage tracks, feed soul points, and view status.

   Only one revenant may be controlled at a time.

   Replaces the old 'animate' spell with a more powerful and
   customizable undead minion system.

See also: HELP REVENANT, HELP REVENANT TRACKS, HELP REVENANT INFUSE
